            "title": "包浩斯上年度盈利急升8.6倍　不派息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15047086&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">包浩斯(00483)公布，截至今年3月底止全年盈利1167.1萬元，按年急升8.61倍，不派息。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內，營業額1.95億元，上升約0.8%，毛利率71.5%，下跌2.7個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15047086-%e5%8c%85%e6%b5%a9%e6%96%af%e4%b8%8a%e5%b9%b4%e5%ba%a6%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e6%80%a5%e5%8d%878-6%e5%80%8d%e3%80%80%e4%b8%8d%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/00483.jpg.webp",
